{"metadata":{"title":"textVariableAnchorOffset","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNSymbolStyleLayer(py)textVariableAnchorOffset","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"textVariableAnchorOffset"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer"]]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSExpression","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When present, this property takes precedence over ","typ